                "content": "Been through a few cycles. \u201cOversupply\u201d headlines don\u2019t equal vacant buildings. Handovers slip, and absorption in JVC remains strong. My Marina/JVC renewals are still up within RERA limits this year. 2026 supply \u2260 2026 occupancy. I\u2019ll price leases by actual handovers and occupancy, not pipeline noise.",
                "created_at": "2026-04-27 07:31:13.622207",
