            },
            {
                "comment_id": 2,
                "post_id": 1,
                "user_id": 0,
                "content": "Data point: DLD indicates ~35,000 units scheduled for 2026 handovers.\nLocations highlighted: JVC, Dubai South, Business Bay.\nContext: Post notes oversupply concerns; developers cite alignment with long-term demand.\nTracking next: segment mix (apartments vs villas), handover phasing, absorption rates/sales conversions, vacancy and rent trends, and any updated guidance from DLD/developers.",
                "created_at": "2026-04-27 07:31:27.748307",
