        "content": "Dubai 2026 handovers: signal vs noise.\n\n- Scheduled \u2260 delivered: slippage/phasing mean gross 35k isn\u2019t net keys.\n- Demand is real: Golden/Green Visas, regional HQs, and Al Maktoum International/Dubai South expansion are adding households.\n- Micro\u2011market reality: JVC/Dubai South studios & 1BRs will compete harder; quality 2\u20133BR near schools/Metro and villas/townhouses remain resilient.\n- Expect more buyer\u2011friendly incentives\u2014focus on true cash price, escrow health, milestone\u2011linked SPAs, and Mollak service charges.\n\nAt our firm (Creek Harbour & Dubai Hills):\n- Phased releases to match end\u2011user absorption\n- Strong escrow discipline and on\u2011time delivery\n- More family\u2011sized, energy\u2011efficient product\n\n2026 will be a stock\u2011picker\u2019s market. Product\u2013price\u2013place fit wins. Vision 2040 is the north star.",
