e quotas, more build‑to‑rent near Metro with essential‑worker allocations, and transparency on vacancy by unit type and rent‑to‑income ratios in JVC/Dubai South/Business Bay. That’s how we improve real affordability.\n\nIf you share your rough budget and unit type, I can outline a community shortlist with lower pipeline and sane service charges so you can compare clearly.'}
